* Drabkin, Artem. ''The Red Air Force at War: Barbarossa and the Retreat to Moscow – Recollections of Fighter Pilots on the Eastern Front''. Barnsley, South Yorkshire, UK: Pen &amp; Sword Military, 2007. ISBN 1-84415-563-3.
* Ford, Daniel. ''Flying Tigers: Claire Chennault and His American Volunteers, 1941-1942''. Washington, DC: HarperCollins|Smithsonian Books, 2007. ISBN 0-06-124655-7.
