      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox royalty
| name = Constantine II
| image = Constantine II of Scotland.jpg
| imgw = 200
| succession = King of Alba
| reign = 900–943
| predecessor = [[Donald II of Scotland|Donald II]]
| successor = [[Malcolm I of Scotland|Malcolm I]]
| issue = [[Indulf]], King of Alba&lt;br /&gt;Cellach&lt;br /&gt;one or more daughters
